{
  "stem": "16163.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, I saw children die then already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember waking up in the morning, and the bed was-- the bed-- the cot was empty.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was told oh, died during the night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It didn't mean anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it was shocking for us children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But after a while, it didn't really mean anything anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then I had one experience in-- it was the early part of 1943.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a transport going of very sick children to Auschwitz then already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't know about Auschwitz, but we knew there was a transport going.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was in that transport already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the doctors hid me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had like a type of a closet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they opened up the closet, put the cot in there, took the door out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "No, they didn't put the door on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They left the door in and put a sign on the door-- typhoid, typhoid patient.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when they came to pick me up, you know, like with the cot to pick me up, they said, oh, this one has typhoid?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the doctor said, look, don't even take her along.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She wouldn't even make it to the train station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's how they saved my life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1943.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it must have been in-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I believe it was in February-- January, February-- in winter '43.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They sent me back to the home, which in between got very, very overcrowded because a lot of children came from Germany, from Austria, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got back there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And little by little, when I felt better, I started to work, like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The sanitary were very bad, but we tried to make the best out of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
